comments: "At Last" can be heard instrumentally in the movie Sun Valley Serenade in three scenes (one with vocalization). The song would re-appear in the 1942 follow-up movie "Orchestra Wives" performed by Glenn Miller and his Orchestra with vocals by Ray Eberle and Pat Friday (lip synced by Lynn Bari in the film).
